title: Spectacular 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom FURNISHED condo!
posting_body: ['To schedule a tour', 'We now book our tour appointments online!', 'Book your appointment today or anytime 24/7:', '<URL>', 'Spectacular 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom FURNISHED condo with views in Sand Point neighborhood', 'Property Description', 'Spectacular 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom FURNISHED 1,015 sf condo with views of the Cascade Mountains and Lake Washington.', ' 2 story unit with vaulted ceilings.', ' Wood burning fireplace in the living room.', ' Private deck great for BBQing and enjoying the sunrise!', ' Super open and airy.', ' The primary bedroom is on the upper floor with private bath.', ' 2nd bedroom is on the entry level with another additional bath.', ' Beautifully maintained and updated.', ' Two parking spaces included #37 and #70.', ' Storage also included #26.', ' Move in ready!!', "Incredible location-close to UW, Children's Hospital, Magnuson Park, Burke Gilman Trail and Mathews Beach!", ' On bus line.', 'Details', 'Availability date:', '08/02/2022', 'Leasing Terms:', "Terms:  1 year lease, 1st, last, one month's rent deposit.", '1 year lease.', 'No smoking.', 'No Pets allowed.', 'Renters insurance is required.', '3:1 income ratio.', '730+ credit score.', 'Co-signers not accepted.', 'Landlord will not accept a comprehensive reusable screening report by a consumer reporting agency.', 'Application fee:', '$46', 'Amenities', 'Parking type:', 'Off-street parking', 'Appliances:', 'Oven/Stove, Fridge, W/D, D/W', 'Heating/cooling:', 'Heat: Baseboard', 'Additional features:', 'Non-Smoking Property', 'Offered by:', 'Windermere Property Management/JMW', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
